
### Upload a Note
POST http://localhost:5000/user-api/notes/upload
Cookie: token=<TOKEN>
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----Boundary

------Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="title"

Operating Systems - Chapter 1
------Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="description"

Introduction to OS concepts: processes, threads, memory management.
------Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="topic"

notes
------Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="note"; filename="sample.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

This is placeholder note content for testing purposes.
Topics covered: Scheduling, Memory, File Systems.
------Boundary--

### Upload a PDF note
POST http://localhost:5000/user-api/notes/upload
Cookie: token=<TOKEN>
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----Boundary2

------Boundary2
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="title"

Data Structures Reference Sheet
------Boundary2
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="description"

Quick reference for arrays, linked lists, trees, graphs.
------Boundary2
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="topic"

pdfs
------Boundary2
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="note"; filename="ds-reference.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

Arrays: O(1) access. Linked Lists: O(n) access. Trees: O(log n) search.
------Boundary2--

