### ──────────────────────────────────────
### 3. Upload a Past Paper (topic: past-papers)
### ──────────────────────────────────────
POST http://localhost:5000/user-api/notes/upload
Cookie: token=<TOKEN>
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----Boundary3

------Boundary3
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="title"

Database Systems — Final Exam 2024
------Boundary3
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="description"

Past paper from May 2024 semester exam covering SQL, Normalization.
------Boundary3
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="topic"

past-papers
------Boundary3
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="note"; filename="dbms-2024.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

Q1: Explain 3NF normalization with an example.
Q2: Write a SQL query to find the second highest salary.
------Boundary3--

